creator: ORANGE GAMES
descriptionHtml:
A SWEET MATCH 3 PUZZLE GAME FEATURING COLORFUL CANDY!

Easy gameplay and vibrant graphics that anyone can enjoy!

Match 3 or more of the same colored candies.
Clear a variety of dynamic levels.
Connect sweet candy to clear levels and unleash beautiful effects.

Experience +3,000 levels of dynamic jewel block action!

[Sweet Candy POP : Match 3 Puzzle Features]
- Simple gameplay featuring fun Match 3 mechanics.
- No hearts - play as much as you want!
- Play anywhere and any time without wi-fi!
- A small game means it's available on all devices.
- Supports 16 languages.

[How To Play?]
- Move and Match 3 or more of the same colored blocks.
- Gather unique items by matching over 4 colors.
- Special blocks crush all your obstacles.
- Clear a variety of fun missions!

This game supports '한국어', 'English', 'Deutsch', 'français', 'Español', 'Русский', 'Italian', 'Portuguese', 'Türkçe', '日本語', '中文简体', '中文繁體', 'ไทย', 'Arabic', 'Bahasa Indonesia', 'Bahasa Malaysia'.

[NOTICE]
- Sweet Candy POP : Match 3 Puzzle's Items are available for purchase in this game. Some paid items may not be refundable depending on the type of item.
- Please be sure to save your phone since it can be initialized when you replace the phone or delete this game.
descriptionShort: Play the funniest match 3 game full of sweet candy.
